<paragraph pageId="397" pageNumber="398">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="397" pageNumber="398">This rarely collected species is known only from the Colorado River valley in southeastern California to western New Mexico (Cibola County, CMNH).</paragraph>
